        "# Práctica 4: Combinaciones"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Objetivo"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Concepto Teórico\n",
        "\n",
        "Las combinaciones se calculan como:\n",
        "\n",
        "\\begin{equation}\n",
        "C(n,k) = \\frac{n!}{k!(n-k)!}\n",
        "\\end{equation}"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Ejercicios\n",
        "\n",
        "- Calcular $C(10,2)$\n",
        "- Calcular $C(100,4)$\n",
        "- Calcular $C(500,3)$"
      ]
    }
  ],
